Support Scalar visualization via TensorBoard. Components as below: 

1) Formatter, interface looks like below:
```
class TBLogger {
   // tag - specifying the type of the event, e.g. "learning rate", "loss", "throughput"
   // scalar - a single float value, e.g. learning rate, loss, etc.
   // returns a Summary protocol buffer containing a single scalar value. 
   // proto definition see  tensorflow/tensorflow/core/framework/summary.proto
   def  scalarSummary(val tag: String, val scalar : Float): String 
    ...
}
```
